# RogueTeamFactory

```js

  isInformalData,

  cardIconPath,
  extraBuffList: [

      num,
      prepositionId,
    }
  ],
  initialEffectList: [
    {
      id,
    }
  ],
  shadePath,
  startTime,
  tabIconPath,
}
```
